IndexTank plugin for vBulletin
http://www.indextank.com

Installation instructions:
1.- Sign up at IndexTank.
2.- Go to your dashboard and create an index.
3.- Download and unzip/untar the last stable version of the IndexTank plugin for vBulletin.
4.- Configure your api url and index name:
    a.- Run the setup.sh script (and follow the instructions)
    b.- Or just edit indextank_nosetup/indextank_plugin.php replacing strings <API_URL> and <INDEX_NAME> by the api url and index name respectively.
5.- Upload the files under the 'indextank' directory (or indextank_nosetup if you edited them manually) to your vbulletin/indextank directory in your web server.
6.- Go to vBulletin's Admin Control Panel >> Plugins & Products >> Download / Upload Plugins and upload the 'indextank-plugin.xml' file that comes with the plugin release.

